  <brief_title>Effectiveness of Two Hyaluronic Acids in Osteoarthritis of the Knee</brief_title>
  <official_title>Single-blind Randomised Pragmatic Trial Comparing the Effectiveness of Two Hyaluronic Acid Viscosupplements, DUROLANE® (Single Injection) Versus HYALGAN® (Three Injections) for Symptomatic Tibiofemoral Osteoarthritis of the Knee.</official_title>
